"""
The pyslk package provides Python wrapper functions for the slk and the
slk_helpers. The slk is the official command line interface (cli) of the
StrongLink system by StrongBox Data Solutions. The slk_helpers was developed
at DKRZ and provides some additional functionality beyond the slk.

* **pyslk.pyslk:** basic wrappers for nearly all slk and slk_helpers commands
* **pyslk.parsers:** extended wrappers for a few slk and slk_helpers commands
* **pyslk.utils:** some utility functions
* **pyslk.exceptions:** one exception class used in this package
"""
